             was indicted for <rs id="t18220703-9-off39" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220703-9-off39" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220703-9-off39" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220703-9-cd40" type="crimeDate">27th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-9-off39 t18220703-9-cd40"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220703-9-victim127" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Bond
                        <interp inst="t18220703-9-victim127" type="surname" value="Bond"></interp>
